info.author: Lars Heuer
info.description:
Package which supports deserialization of the Linear Topic Maps (LTM) syntax.

This package can be used to add a LTM 1.3 reader to the `tm
<http://pypi.python.org/pypi/tm>`_ package.
info.name: tm.mio.reader.ltm
info.summary: Linear Topic Maps (LTM) reader for the Topic Maps package
